 |                             [GAME INFORMATION]                             |
 |                                                                            |
 | Use dual styluses for real sports moments that deliver an addicting        |
 | challenge for any athlete!                                                 |
 | The first ever dual touch action sports game, DualPenSports provides a     |
 | fresh gameplay experience that allows consumers to feel more like they're  |
 | playing real sports with the use of up to two styluses. Fun, exciting, and |
 | accessible to everyone, DualPenSports' two hand coordination challenges    |
 | players in new ways, providing an instant edge in the handheld and casual  |
 | gaming markets!                                                            |
